 (35,1,21,'','关于2018上半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于2018上半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">受上海市教育委员会委托，同时根据上海市相关的工作要求，现由上海市托幼协会按照上海市教育评估院组织专家评审意见，将</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">上半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单进行公示。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">如有不同意见需反映，请于</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">12</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">日之前将有关情况以书面形式寄（送）上海市托幼协会。地址：石门二路</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">199</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">弄</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">404</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">室，邮编</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">200041</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">。单位反</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">映情况须加盖公章，个人反映情况请留真实姓名及联系方式。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">具体名单见附件：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">上半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 373px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">上海市托幼协会</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">9</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">29</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">日</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><br/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 2px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://118.31.3.95/fileserver/lib/extjs/ueditor/utf8-jsp/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif\"/><a title=\"2018上半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); font-size: 12px;\" href=\"http://118.31.3.95/fileserver/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20181017/1539756427252059507.pdf\">2018上半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示.pdf</a></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>',0,'2018-10-17 13:47:27',6,-1,-1,-1,'2018-10-17 13:47:27',-1,'2018-10-17 14:46:23',-1,'ID',NULL,NULL,NULL),
 (36,0,21,'','上海市教育委员会关于公布2016年至2017年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单的通知','<p style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: red; letter-spacing: 12px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 48px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上海市教育委员会文件</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 文鼎大标宋简; font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 1px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; line-height: 37px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沪教委基〔2018〕51号</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><hr color=\"#ff000\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/><p></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 1px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; line-height: 37px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 1px; border: currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; line-height: 37px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px;\">上海市教育委员会关于公布2016年至2017年</span><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 40px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单的通知</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 40px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 40px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">各区教育局、市教育评估院：</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 40px; text-indent: 40px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">根据《上海市教育委员会关于上海市托幼协会对本市一级幼儿园、托儿所资质进行审核的通知》（沪教委基〔2002〕69号）和《上海市教育委员会关于进一步规范本市托幼园所办学等级评估办法的意见》（沪教委基〔2003〕87号）要求，经对2016年上半年、下半年和2017年上半年、下半年申报上海市一级幼儿园的单位进行验收，现认定徐汇区印象幼儿园等51所幼儿园为上海市一级幼儿园（具体名单见附件）。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 40px; text-indent: 40px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">希望上述幼儿园在所在区教育局领导下，再接再厉，进一步加强内涵建设，不断提高办园质量，发挥示范辐射作用。希望各区教育局继续加强对区域内托幼园所的指导和管理，进一步提高托幼园所整体办园水平。</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font: 400 16px/16px sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p></p><p style=\