; font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\">200041</span></p><p style=\"margin: 13px 2px 0px 35px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 28, 28); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;\">三、申报材料递交截至时间</span></p><p style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 72px;\"><span style=\"margin: 532px auto auto 851px; left: 0px; width: 253px; height: 234px; font-family: 宋体; position: absolute; z-index: -1879050249;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(49, 49, 49); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">上半年为 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\">3 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">月 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\">30 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(49, 49, 49); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">日止，下半年为 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\">9 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">月 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\">29 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">日止。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 72px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 72px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img width=\"235\" height=\"217\" title=\"1539829664688071167.jpg\" style=\"width: 105px; height: 89px;\" alt=\"托幼章.jpg\" src=\"http://118.31.3.95/fileserver/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181018/1539829664688071167.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Times New Roman;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Times New Roman;\"><br/></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Times New Roman;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 2px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://118.31.3.95/fileserver/lib/extjs/ueditor/utf8-jsp/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif\"/><a title=\"关于2018下半年上海市幼儿园分等定级评估申报工作的通知(1).pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); font-size: 12px;\" href=\"http://118.31.3.95/fileserver/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20181018/1539829247469068403.pdf\">关于2018下半年上海市幼儿园分等定级评估申报工作的通知(1).pdf</a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Times New Roman;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family:; font-size: 17px;\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 72px;\"><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 72px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 72px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 66, 66); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 17px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>',0,'2018-10-18 10:20:53',6,-1,-1,-1,'2018-10-18 10:20:53',-1,'2018-10-18 10:31:32',-1,'ID',NULL,NULL,NULL),
 (39,1,21,'','关于2018下半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于2018下半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">受上海市教育委员会委托，同时根据上海市相关的工作要求，现由上海市托幼协会按照上海市教育评估院组织专家评审意见，将新申报并通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园进行公示。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">如有不同意见需要反映，请于</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">12</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">28</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">日之前将有关情况以书面形式寄（送）上海市托幼协会。地址：石门二路</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">199</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">弄</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">404</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">室，邮编</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">200041</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">。单位反</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">映情况要加盖公章，个人反映情况请留真实姓名及联系方式。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">具体名单见附件：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">年下半年新申报上海市一级幼儿园通过验收的幼儿园名单</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 373px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img width=\"320\" height=\"296\" title=\"1545023967479006041.jpg\" style=\"width: 154px; height: 142px;\" alt=\"捕获.jpg\" src=\"http://www.shstyxh.com/fileserver/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181217/1545023967479006041.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 2px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://www.shstyxh.com/fileserver/lib/extjs/ueditor/utf8-jsp/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif\"/><a title=\"2018年下半年新申报上海市一级幼儿园通过验收的幼儿园名单.doc\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 204); font-size: 12px;\" href=\"http://www.shstyxh.com/fileserver/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20181217/1545024591824013140.doc\">2018下半年通过验收的上海市一级幼儿园名单公示.doc</a></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 47px; text-indent: 392px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>',80,'2018-12-17 13:46:31',2,-1,-1,-1,'2018-12-17 13:46:31',-1,'2018-12-24 10:24:10',-1,'ID',NULL,NULL,NULL);
