 (1215,35,1,'','2018年基础教育国家级教学成果奖','','',NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p><p>热烈祝贺上海学前教育四项教学成果荣获2018年基础教育国家级教学成果奖！(具体见下表)为让广大会员单位老师尽早了解学习到获奖成果内容，本期简报特刊出他们的成果报告(简版)。</p><table width=\"658\" style=\"width: 658px; height: 176px;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"47\" style=\"padding: 0px 7px; border: 1px solid windowtext; border-image: none; background-color: transparent;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">序号</span></span></p></td><td width=\"66\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; border-image: none; background-color: transparent;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">授奖项</span></span></p></td><td width=\"255\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; border-image: none; background-color: transparent;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">成果名称</span></span></p></td><td width=\"125\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; border-image: none; background-color: transparent;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">成果完成者</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 54px;\"><td width=\"47\" height=\"54\" style=\"border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext; padding: 0px 7px; border-image: none; background-color: transparent;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">1</span></span></p></td><td width=\"66\" height=\"54\" style=\